= Intraparty Influence

Now that we as the reformists have gained power in the party, we have the chance to consolidate our hold over various segments of the party.

- @q0: Increase reformist presence in the grassroots and the youth wing.
- @q1: Propagate Social Democratic ideals among the electorate.
- @q3: Strengthen our hold over the parliament delegates.
- @q4: Sponsor intellectuals aligned with the left of center cause.
- @q5: Place Social Democrats in positions of power within our municipalities.

